value: Control basic functionality by swiping and pinching on window titlebars.
Most Window and Snapping gestures also work in Mission Control & App Exposé.
Pinch in twice to quit an application.
Pinch in once to close a window.
Swipe down once to minimize a window.
Pinch out or tap, hold and swipe up to enter or exit fullscreen mode.
Double tap with the general modifier to hide all windows of an application. Use the secondary modifier to hide all other apps.
Tap, hold and swipe or use the general modifier to move a window between Mission Control spaces.
